     fhir:Narrative.status [ fhir:value "extensions" ] ;
     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet OperationssaarKomplikationerKAR</b></p><a name=\"OperationssaarKomplikationerKAR\"> </a><a name=\"hcOperationssaarKomplikationerKAR\"> </a><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-Complications.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/Complications</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-Complications.html#Complications-hematoma\">hematoma</a></td><td>operationskrævende hæmatom</td><td>Surgery required hematoma / operationskrævende hæmatom</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-Complications.html#Complications-lymph_leakage\">lymph_leakage</a></td><td>lymfesiven over 2 døgn (forlænger indlæggelsen)</td><td>Lymph leakage over 2 days / lymfesiven over 2 døgn (forlænger indlæggelsen)</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-Complications.html#Complications-necrosis\">necrosis</a></td><td>operationskrævende randnekrose</td><td>Surgery required necrosis / operationskrævende randnekrose</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-Complications.html#Complications-lymphocele\">lymphocele</a></td><td>operationskrævende lymfocele</td><td>Surgery required lymphocele / operationskrævende lymfocele</td></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-GenericValues.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/GenericValues</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td>